sequenceDiagram
    actor Z as Zákazník
    participant F as Frontend
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant O as Order Service
    participant P as Product Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Pay as Payment Service
    participant N as Notification Service

    Z->>F: Klikne "Kúpiť"
    F->>G: POST /orders
    G->>O: createOrder()
    O->>P: overenie dostupnosti
    P-->>O: OK
    O->>DB: uloženie objednávky
    O->>Pay: autorizácia platby
    Pay-->>O: výsledok
    O->>N: notifikácia
    O-->>G: potvrdenie
    G-->>F: 201 Created